00178     return name >= XED_OPERAND_REG0 && name <= XED_OPERAND_REG15;

00185 static XED_INLINE xed_uint_t xed_operand_is_memory_addressing_register(xed_operand_enum_t name) {
00186     return  ( name == XED_OPERAND_BASE0 || 
00187               name == XED_OPERAND_INDEX ||
00188               name == XED_OPERAND_SEG0  ||
00189               name == XED_OPERAND_BASE1 || 
00190               name == XED_OPERAND_SEG1 );

00316 static XED_INLINE xed_uint32_t xed_inst_get_attribute(const xed_inst_t* p, 
00317                                                       xed_attribute_enum_t attr) {
00318     const xed_uint64_t one = 1;
00319     if (p->_attributes & (one<<attr)) 
00320         return 1;
00321     return 0;
00322 }
